@startuml
title Viaverse Taxonomy Version / Category Mapping — State Diagram

[*] --> VERSION_DRAFT
VERSION_DRAFT --> VERSION_IN_REVIEW : submit
VERSION_IN_REVIEW --> VERSION_PUBLISHED : approve
VERSION_IN_REVIEW --> VERSION_DRAFT : changes
VERSION_PUBLISHED --> VERSION_RETIRED : new version

[*] --> UNMAPPED
UNMAPPED --> AI_SUGGESTED : AI suggestion
AI_SUGGESTED --> MAPPED : user/admin confirms
UNMAPPED --> MAPPED : manual select
MAPPED --> REMAP_REQUIRED : taxonomy changed
REMAP_REQUIRED --> MAPPED : migration mapping
MAPPED --> MAPPING_ARCHIVED : source deleted

VERSION_RETIRED --> [*]
MAPPING_ARCHIVED --> [*]

note bottom
Existing requests/providers must not break when taxonomy changes.
Remap-required state and migration mapping protect old data and search continuity.
end note
@enduml
